 50 Cent and Girlfriend Cuban Link Award-winning rapper cum filmmaker, Curtis Jackson, popularly known in the media circles as “50 Cent” has gifted his girlfriend, Cuban Link a 2021 Mercedes Maybach Benz. 50 Cent has joined the list of celebrity boyfriends who have surprised their partners with expensive gifts this Christmas. The 2021 Mercedes-Maybach GLS he bought for her is the range-topping version of the third-generation SUV, launched in 2019 for the 2020 model year. It is fancied up GLS with extra luxury features, exclusive appointments, and a unique drivetrain. View this post on Instagram A post shared by 50 Cent (@50cent)